Putting Palantir in charge of #Covid19UK data store a pretty stupid idea too when trust in UK Governments already so low.
https://t.co/QzphwUmjp7

Difficult to see how trust in vaccination programmes can be repaired after this. Making it illegal to accept any funding from Bill & Melinda Gates might be a good place to start. #Covid19UK  https://t.co/OXgIlZjfTl
